  <brief_title>Prescription Patterns, Resource Utilization &amp; Costs - Add-on Therapy With Anti Dipeptidyl Peptidase-IVs vs Rosiglitazone</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prescription Patterns, Resource Utilization &amp; Costs - Add-on Therapy With Anti Dipeptidyl Peptidase-IVs vs Rosiglitazone</official_title>
