  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This retrospective database study analyzed resource utilization and costs associated with
      sitagliptin (STG) in comparison with rosiglitazone (RSG) added to metformin (MET) monotherapy
      among adults with a diagnosis of diabetes who were continuously enrolled in a large US
      healthcare plan.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
